OL,6,FA jury at the Old Bailey took eight
OL,7,Fhours of deliberations to find Motin,
OL,8,F59, from St Petersburg, guilty of
OL,9,Fmanslaughter by gross negligence.
OL,11,FDet Ch Supt Craig Nicholson, of
OL,12,FHumberside Police, said it was a
OL,13,F"simple, senseless tragedy".
OL,15,FHe said: "It's a miracle that there
OL,16,Fweren't more fatalities or serious
OL,17,Finjuries.
