OL,6,F"Similarly, this could have been a
OL,7,Fhuge environmental catastrophe. The
OL,8,FSolong burned for eight days following
OL,9,Fthe collision.
OL,11,F"There were people on the deck of the
OL,12,FStena Immaculate at the point of
OL,13,Fimpact. One crew member was up a mast
OL,14,Fchanging a light fitting."
OL,16,FThe trial heard the 130m-long Solong,
OL,17,Fwhich weighed 7,852 tonnes, had
OL,18,Fdeparted from Grangemouth in Scotland
OL,19,Fon 9 March bound for the port of
OL,20,FRotterdam in Holland.
