OL,6,FWith a 14-strong crew, it was carrying
OL,7,Fmainly alcoholic spirits and some
OL,8,Fhazardous substances, including empty
OL,9,Fbut unclean sodium cyanide containers.
OL,11,FThe Stena Immaculate, with a crew of
OL,12,F23, was 183m long and was transporting
OL,13,Fmore than 220,000 barrels of aviation
OL,14,Ffuel from Greece to the UK.
OL,16,FWith both ships laden with flammable
OL,17,Fcargo, the danger in the event of a
OL,18,Fcollision was obvious, jurors were
OL,19,Ftold.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/11
