OL,6,FDramatic CCTV footage captured the
OL,7,Fmoment both ships were consumed in a
OL,8,Fmassive blaze ignited by leaking fuel
OL,9,Ffrom the Stena Immaculate.
OL,11,FThe shocked crew about the US tanker
OL,12,Freacted instantly, saying: "Holy
OL,13,Fs***... what just hit us... a
OL,14,Fcontainer ship... this is no drill,
OL,15,Fthis is no drill, fire fire fire, we
OL,16,Fhave had a collision."
