OL,6,FProsecutor Julia Faure Walker had told
OL,7,Fjurors: "It would have been blindingly
OL,8,Fobvious to him that he had pressed the
OL,9,Fwrong button, and how to rectify it if
OL,10,Fthat is what happened.
OL,12,F"The reality is that he did nothing to
OL,13,Favoid collision. Instead he launched
OL,14,Finto a problem that had never occurred
OL,15,Fon the Solong.
OL,17,F"There were no mechanical or
OL,18,Felectronic difficulties on the Solong.
OL,19,FThe rudder was working. The only thing
OL,20,Fthat was not working on March 10 2025
OL,21,Fwas the man in the dock."
