OL,6,FShe said jurors may conclude that
OL,7,FMotin had a "lax attitude" and
OL,8,F"thought he knew better than anyone
OL,9,Felse".
OL,11,FShe pointed to the fact that he had
OL,12,Fswitched off the Solong's bridge
OL,13,Fnavigation watch alert system (BNWAS),
OL,14,Fwhich was designed to ensure there is
OL,15,Fsomeone physically on the bridge and
OL,16,Fawake.
OL,18,FThe prosecution said his failures were
OL,19,F"exceptionally bad, they amount to
OL,20,Fgross negligence".
